text: Schloss Lenzburg (also known as Lenzburg Castle) is a castle that was started above the older part of the town of Lenzburg in the Canton of Aargau, Switzerland. It is one of the oldest castles in Switzerland. Category:Castles in Europe Category:11th-century buildings and structures Category:Buildings and structures in Switzerland Category:Lenzburg District
title: Schloss Lenzburg
